In Engliſh.

This Coffin doth contain the Bones of venerable Bede;



                           Chriſt to the Maker ſence did give, and to the Giver Gold;

One Peter fram'd the work, the coſt Biſhop Hugo made;

So Peter, and Hugo, Patrons both, St. Bede inclos'd in mould.
